STATE
v.
Teon Jamell WILLIAMS. No. 8P16-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 17, 2016. Teon Jamell Williams, Tabor City, for Williams, Teon Jamell. Joseph L. Hyde, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Sarah Kirkman, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 7th of January 2016 by Defendant to Proceed In Forma Pauperis:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th of March 2016."
